file.name: index.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: "api 测试"
  description: "测试"
  version: "1.0.0"
servers:
  - url: http://localhost:1234
    description: 默认版本
paths:
  /getHello:
    get:
      summary: hello 请求
      tags:
        - "hello"
      description: ""
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: id
          description: 传一个id过去
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
      responses:
        200:
          description: 成功
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
components:
  schemas:
    ApiResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        code: { type: integer, default: 200, description: "响应码" }
        msg: { type: string, default: "success", description: "响应描述" }
        data: { type: object, description: "自定义数据" }
